# Configuration Contract: Docusaurus Branding Elements

## Overview
This contract defines the structure and validation rules for the Docusaurus configuration elements that will be modified for the book branding.

## Configuration Schema

### Root Level
```json
{
  "title": "Docusaurus Book Branding Configuration",
  "type": "object",
  "required": ["themeConfig"],
  "properties": {
    "themeConfig": {
      "$ref": "#/definitions/ThemeConfig"
    }
  }
}
```

### Theme Configuration
```json
{
  "definitions": {
    "ThemeConfig": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "navbar": {
          "$ref": "#/definitions/NavbarConfig"
        },
        "footer": {
          "$ref": "#/definitions/FooterConfig"
        },
        "favicon": {
          "type": "string",
          "pattern": "^/.*\\.(ico|png|jpg|jpeg|svg)$",
          "description": "Path to favicon file, must be ASCII-safe and relative to static directory"
        },
        "metadata": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/MetadataItem"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "NavbarConfig": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["title"],
      "properties": {
        "title": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1,
          "maxLength": 100,
          "description": "Book title to display in navbar"
        },
        "logo": {
          "$ref": "#/definitions/LogoConfig"
        },
        "items": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/NavItem"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "FooterConfig": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["copyright"],
      "properties": {
        "copyright": {
          "type": "string",
          "minLength": 1,
          "description": "Copyright notice for the book"
        },
        "logo": {
          "$ref": "#/definitions/LogoConfig"
        },
        "links": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/FooterLink"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "LogoConfig": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["alt", "src"],
      "properties": {
        "alt": {
          "type": "string",
          "description": "Alternative text for accessibility"
        },
        "src": {
          "type": "string",
          "pattern": "^/.*\\.(png|jpg|jpeg|svg|webp)$",
          "description": "Path to logo file, must be ASCII-safe and relative to static directory"
        },
        "srcDark": {
          "type": "string",
          "pattern": "^/.*\\.(png|jpg|jpeg|svg|webp)$",
          "description": "Path to dark mode logo file (optional)"
        }
      }
    },
    "MetadataItem": {
      "type": "object",
      "required": ["name", "content"],
      "properties": {
        "name": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "content": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    },
    "NavItem": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "type": {
          "type": "string",
          "enum": ["doc", "docsVersion", "link"]
        },
        "label": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "to": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "href": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    },
    "FooterLink": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "title": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "items": {
          "type": "array",
          "items": {
            "$ref": "#/definitions/FooterLinkItem"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "FooterLinkItem": {
      "type": "object",
      "properties": {
        "label": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "to": {
          "type": "string"
        },
        "href": {
          "type": "string"
        }
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Validation Rules

### ASCII Compliance
- All string values must contain only ASCII characters (0-127)
- All file paths must use forward slashes and be relative to the static directory
- File names must not contain special characters or spaces

### Accessibility Requirements
- All image elements must have appropriate alt text
- Color contrast ratios must meet WCAG 2.1 AA standards
- Navigation elements must be keyboard accessible

### Performance Requirements
- All asset paths must point to optimized files
- Logo files must be under 200KB
- Favicon files must be under 50KB
- All pages must load in under 3 seconds

## Implementation Checklist
- [ ] Navbar title updated to book title
- [ ] Logo in navbar updated to book logo
- [ ] Footer copyright updated to book copyright
- [ ] Favicon updated to book favicon
- [ ] Metadata updated to reflect book content
- [ ] All paths are ASCII-safe
- [ ] All assets are accessible
- [ ] All assets meet performance requirements